            <title>黃金商場通告指媒體「亂衰」聲譽，未經許可下不準拍攝 + 將加緊巡視</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/21/shooting-work-is-not-allowed-in-golden-computer-arcade/hottopic/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=shooting-work-is-not-allowed-in-golden-computer-arcade</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/21/shooting-work-is-not-allowed-in-golden-computer-arcade/hottopic/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Ngan Ivan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 21 Jun 2024 08:52:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[生活娛樂]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[黃金電腦商場]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1244951</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">黃金電腦商場近日被發現在場內張貼通告，重申商場內一向禁止所有未經許可的拍攝工作。通告中指出有媒體未經許可在商場內拍攝，並發佈針對性的照片和報道。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1244984" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_1208-466x580.jpg" alt="黃金電腦商場不準拍攝工作通告" width="466" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_1208-466x580.jpg 466w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/img_1208.jpg 540w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 466px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3723201/page/1">LIHKG</a></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1244982 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718959184-694x519.jpg" alt="黃金電腦商場" width="694" height="519" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718959184-694x519.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/06/unwire-1718959184.jpg 1203w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲圖片來源：<a href="https://www.freeguider.com/hk/venues/Golden-computer-arcade-disable-shopping">Free Guider</a></p><p style="font-weight: 400;">早在三個星期前本台就曾經到場內拍攝，更與場內 4 間電腦店舖的代表進行訪談，討論俗稱為「腦場」的黃金電腦商場的發展。訪談以「腦場」文化和香港砌機業的興衰為主題。</p><div class="epyt-video-wrapper"><iframe loading="lazy"  style="display: block; margin: 0px auto;"  id="_ytid_16868"  width="590" height="332"  data-origwidth="590" data-origheight="332" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/HxwBEsC6eys?enablejsapi=1&#038;autoplay=0&#038;cc_load_policy=0&#038;cc_lang_pref=&#038;iv_load_policy=1&#038;loop=0&#038;modestbranding=1&#038;rel=0&#038;fs=1&#038;playsinline=1&#038;autohide=1&#038;theme=light&#038;color=white&#038;controls=1&#038;" class="__youtube_prefs__  epyt-is-override  no-lazyload" title="YouTube player"  allow="fullscreen; accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen data-no-lazy="1" data-skipgform_ajax_framebjll=""></iframe></div><p style="font-weight: 400;">黃金商場張貼的通告，將人流冷清、多個空置舖位的問題歸究於媒體的惡意報道和唱衰，使商場的聲譽受到損害。黃金電腦商場呼籲場內人士一旦發現未經許可的拍攝請立即通知管理處，並將會安排保安加緊場內的巡視工作。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">資料及圖片來源：<a href="https://lihkg.com/thread/3723201/page/1">LIHKG</a></p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/06/21/shooting-work-is-not-allowed-in-golden-computer-arcade/hottopic/">黃金商場通告指媒體「亂衰」聲譽，未經許可下不準拍攝 + 將加緊巡視</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/06/21/shooting-work-is-not-allowed-in-golden-computer-arcade/hottopic/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
